s/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我一直都想練好啲身型，但成日得個講字。"},{"pid":"360769c36bd828dd86bcfe3d10dece992aafa606","tid":166194,"uid":70292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T02:56:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唉自己性格點解咁內向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打平時有咩興趣</blockquote><br />\n我興趣唔係太常人平時既興趣，正常男仔打下波睇波玩lol,fifa等，我就比較鐘意游下水，睇下戲，睇下鞋，行山，踩單車，研究天文地理，所以冇乜朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中意游水都無骨友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁性格呢D真係應該好難幫到你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc7b6110b0984aaf288085dc9acfce80dbb335f","tid":166194,"uid":45439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T02:59:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唉自己性格點解咁內向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打平時有咩興趣</blockquote><br />\n我興趣唔係太常人平時既興趣，正常男仔打下波睇波玩lol,fifa等，我就比較鐘意游下水，睇下戲，睇下鞋，行山，踩單車，研究天文地理，所以冇乜朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中意游水都無骨友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁性格呢D真係應該好難幫到你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實都係因為我好少主動約人：嗨，搵日一齊游下水。"},{"pid":"1f8d22dd1956cf7ae099fdfd337de353365823b3","tid":166194,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T03:00:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><bloc